text: "Above and Beyond" also known as Above and Beyond (The Call of Love) is a 1960 song by country singer Buck Owens and went to number 3 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs charts. In 1989, it was covered by Rodney Crowell. It was taken from his fifth studio album Diamonds & Dirt. It topped the country single charts in both Canada and the United States.
